    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Shoppers Stop Consulting Pvt Ltd. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Visual Merchandiser to strengthen our Jabalpur-based team.\n\nAbout Shoppers Stop Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nShoppers Stop Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in Category Management\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Referral bonus program\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Shoppers Stop Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
